<span id="freeTextContainer15388783355774608802">This book explained the basic concepts of physics, and major breakthroughs in the field over the years in such an effortlessly poetic way, that I couldn&apos;t help but be drawn in and understand them a little bit better. Really fantastic stuff.</span>
  <span id="freeText15388783355774608802" style="display:none">This book explained the basic concepts of physics, and major breakthroughs in the field over the years in such an effortlessly poetic way, that I couldn't help but be drawn in and understand them a little bit better. Really fantastic stuff.</span>
